{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b5b68c9a4a","title":"关于回国后沿途接待问题的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"84b9c3e3c5","index":0,"year":1950,"month":2,"day":23,"articleId":"b5b68c9a4a"}],"tags":[{"id":"af71a4eedb","name":"高岗","type":"人物"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"334f319f35","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b5b68c9a4a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指王橡祥，当时任中国驻苏联大使。"},{"id":"07af7e474b","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b5b68c9a4a","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高岗，当时任中央人民政府副主席兼东北人民政府主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"04f5e28cff","type":"title","text":"关于回国后沿途接待问题的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b5b68c9a4a"},{"id":"334f319f35","type":"paragraph","text":"王大使，转刘少奇、高岗P二同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b5b68c9a4a"},{"id":"07af7e474b","type":"paragraph","text":"我们一行因沿途参观今廿三日可到伊尔库次克。计廿六日可到满洲里，尔后拟于海拉尔、齐齐哈尔、哈尔滨、长春、四平街、铁岭各停留一二小时至三四小时，到沈阳拟停留一二天。请高岗同志通知上述各地负责同志保守秘密，每处只要少数负责干部迎接招待，不要使多数人知道，无其不要公开发表消息。尔后至打虎山、锦州、山海关、唐山、塘活、天津，均拟略作参观，均要保守秘密。到北京下车时，亦只要有少数党内党外人士（一百人左右）至车站迎接，不要便多数人知道，待到北京后方才发表消息。请照此布置为盼。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b5b68c9a4a"},{"id":"f495b50e8d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b5b68c9a4a"},{"id":"5cd9f742cb","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b5b68c9a4a"}],"page":{"id":"20a391b8c8","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"b5b68c9a4a","start":216,"end":216}}}},"__N_SSG":true}